{"noun":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/35/df/95314_crt_933O1.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/35/df/95314_crt_933O1.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/35/df/95314_crt_933O1.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/35/df/95314_crt_933O1.jpg"},"name":"劉備","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/52/6c/4374_seiyu_anidb.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/52/6c/4374_seiyu_anidb.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/52/6c/4374_seiyu_anidb.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/52/6c/4374_seiyu_anidb.jpg"},"name":"中村大樹","short_summary":"","career":["artist","seiyu"],"id":4374,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":95314},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/57/c5/95315_crt_UZFl9.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/57/c5/95315_crt_UZFl9.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/57/c5/95315_crt_UZFl9.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/57/c5/95315_crt_UZFl9.jpg"},"name":"張飛","relation":"主角","actors":[{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/ae/9c/4016_prsn_KYg1E.jpg?r=1514563577","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/ae/9c/4016_prsn_KYg1E.jpg?r=1514563577","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/ae/9c/4016_prsn_KYg1E.jpg?r=1514563577","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/ae/9c/4016_prsn_KYg1E.jpg?r=1514563577"},"name":"藤原啓治","short_summary":"日本声优，生于东京，1980年代入行。\r\n代表作品有《十二国记》乍骁宗、《钢之炼金术师》马斯·休斯、《交响诗篇》霍兰德、《蜡笔小新》野原广志、《青之驱魔师》藤本狮郎、《银魂》服部全藏、《潮与虎》苍月紫暮、《传颂之物虚伪的假面》哈克、《玉子市场》北白川豆大等。\r\n2016年8月，因为健康状态不良而退出电视动画的录音，所属事务所并没有公布藤原启治的病因。\r\n2017年6月16日，AIR AGENCY事务所宣布藤原启治正式回归。\r\n2020年4月12日，藤原启治因癌症去世，终年55岁。\r\n\r\n频繁演出『机兽新世纪 ZOIDS』『钢之炼金术师』『天保异闻 妖奇士』『血战』『机动战士钢弹00』等人气动画\r\n代表作有蜡笔小新(野原广志)、交响诗篇艾蕾卡7(霍兰德)、钢之炼金术师(休斯)、天保异闻 妖奇士(龙导往压)、机兽新世纪(阿帕因)、BLOOD+(内森)、校园迷糊大王(旁白)、KERORO军曹(旁白、波尔森山)等\r\n所属经历为文学座剧团附属演剧研究所→剧团木山事务所→贤事务所。然后在2006年11月创立自己的事务所AIR AGENCY\r\n和同样为声优的子安武人、樱井孝宏、三木真一郎有相当的交情。\r\n跟楢桥美纪和矢岛晶子一起出席猜谜节目时，被说『广志的台词就「我回来了」这句话是最多的』。\r\n由于野原广志给人的印象太强烈、在2ちゃんねる和したらば掲示板等论坛中、藤原所演出的角色大多被叫「广志」。\r\n在『蜡笔小新』的动画系列中，电视上许多政治家或明星有不伦恋或出柜等新闻都使用藤原的名字（有台词的场合也是他配音的）。\r\n小时候的家教相当严格，大部分的时间没办法看动画，所以只能看『3时のあなた』英语教学节目。\r\n\r\n经常配大叔角色。\r\n除了大叔类型的角色外，因为其低沉性感的声系，偶尔也会帮美型男类型的角色配音，包括有钢铁神兵(龙)、棋灵王(绪方精次)、十二国记(骁宗)、圣魔之血(伊萨克‧费南度‧冯‧坎柏菲)、奇迹列车(车掌)和妖怪少爷(奴良鲤伴)等。\r\n藤原启治生前也是美国影星小罗伯特·唐尼的专用日语吹替。","career":["seiyu"],"id":4016,"type":1,"locked":false}],"type":1,"id":95315},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/c8/6f/122954_crt_7kLl6.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c8/6f/122954_crt_7kLl6.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/c8/6f/122954_crt_7kLl6.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/c8/6f/122954_crt_7kLl6.jpg"},"name":"関羽","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":122954},{"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/a9/46/123286_crt_zG4gG.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a9/46/123286_crt_zG4gG.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/a9/46/123286_crt_zG4gG.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/a9/46/123286_crt_zG4gG.jpg"},"name":"諸葛亮","relation":"主角","actors":[],"type":1,"id":123286}],"detail":[{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"male","birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/35/df/95314_crt_933O1.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/35/df/95314_crt_933O1.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/35/df/95314_crt_933O1.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/crt/l/35/df/95314_crt_933O1.jpg"},"summary":"","name":"劉備","infobox":[{"key":"简体中文名","value":"刘备"},{"key":"别名","value":[]},{"key":"性别","value":"男"}],"stat":{"comments":2,"collects":2},"id":95314,"locked":false,"type":1,"nsfw":false},{"birth_mon":null,"gender":"male","birth_day":null,"birth_year":null,"blood_type":null,"images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/crt/l/a9/46/123286_crt_zG4gG.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a9/46/123286_crt_zG4gG.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/a9/46/123286_crt_zG